0to%20the%20national%20capital%20against%20the%20Bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%2050%2C000%20people%20were%20planning%20to%20march%20from%20Rajouri%20to%20Delhi%20today%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20Bills.%20However%2C%20authorities%20foiled%20the%20march%20and%20restrictions%20similar%20to%20the%20day%20when%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down%20were%20imposed%20in%20Rajouri.%20This%20is%20undemocratic%2C%20but%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20raise%20our%20voice%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zahid%20Parwaz%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20Gujjar%20leader%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Gujjar%20Bakarwal%20Youth%20Welfare%20Conference%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(Rajouri)%20S.P.N.%20Amritpal%20Singh%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20despite%20repeated%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20that%20security%20personnel%20set%20up%20checkpoints%20and%20blockades%20on%20roads%20in%20Thanamandi%20and%20adjoining%20areas%20of%20Rajouri%20district%20on%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20where%20passenger%20and%20private%20vehicles%20were%20frisked%20and%20all%20those%20who%20were%20planning%20to%20join%20the%20march%20against%20the%20Bills%20were%20deboarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98The%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98The%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%E2%80%99%20were%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session%20in%20July%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20notification%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20said%20that%20the%20two%20Bills%2C%20which%20will%20also%20extend%20political%20reservation%20to%20the%20Paharis%2C%20are%20listed%20under%20%E2%80%98Legislative%20Business%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1981907%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Clikely%20to%20