0J%26amp%3BK%20legislature%20under%20the%20ST%20category%20(10%25%20in%20J%26amp%3BK)%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Gadda%20Brahmin%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Koli%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Paddari%20Tribe%E2%80%99%20communities%2C%20thereby%20shrinking%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20already-defined%20ST%20communities%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFeeling%20dismayed%2C%20the%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20parts%20of%20Jammu%20as%20well%20as%20on%20social%20media%20to%20vent%20their%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESporadic%20protests%20also%20broke%20out%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20Jammu%20division%20against%20the%20Bills.%20At%20the%20University%20of%20Jammu%2C%20a%20protest%20was%20held%20on%20Wednesday%20(December%206)%20by%20tribal%20students%2C%20prompting%20the%20police%20to%20enter%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20protest%20verified%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20policemen%20in%20riot%20gear%20striding%20around%20the%20university%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPolice%20entered%20in%20Jammu%20University%20campus%20and%20started%20arresting%20Gujjar%20Bakerwal%20students%20as%20they%20were%20doing%20Protest%20against%20the%20Bills%20in%20which%20all%20elite%20classes%20being%20added%20into%20ST%20Status.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FABVbv7Er2w%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FABVbv7Er2w%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Zahid%20Parwaz%20Choudhary%20(%40ZahidParwaz)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZahidParwaz%2Fstatus%2F1732372618018472306%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20video%20shot%20on%20Wednesday%20showed%20the%20protesting%20students%20shouting%20anti-police%20slogans%20and%20taking%20out%20a%20candlelight%20march%20while%20alleg