0Jammu%20regions%20with%20their%20livestock%20of%20buffaloes%2C%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20the%20Paharis%20are%20a%20socially%20stratified%20community%20with%20caste%20and%20other%20ethnic%20divisions%20who%20are%20joined%20by%20the%20thread%20of%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20passed%2C%20the%20Bills%20will%20be%20the%20first%20of%20their%20kind%20to%20not%20only%20grant%20tribal%20status%20to%20a%20linguistic%20group%2C%20but%20also%20provide%20them%20with%20political%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20two%20Bills%20on%20ST%20status%20for%20Paharis%2C%20three%20more%20Bills%20on%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20will%20restructure%20the%20reservation%20rules%20and%20representation%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20during%20the%20ongoing%20parliament%20session%20which%20started%20on%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribal%20groups%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20since%20December%2025%2C%202019%2C%20when%20a%20delegation%20of%20Paharis%20met%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20sought%20ST%20status%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20the%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakkerwals%20have%20been%20organising%20events%2C%20candlelight%20marches%2C%20protests%20and%20even%20a%20couple%20of%20%3Cem%3Emahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3Es%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20express%20their%20anger%20against%20the%20likely%20grant%20of%20ST%20status%20to%20Paharis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202020%2C%20the%20Paharis%20were%20given%20a%204%25%20reservation%20in%20the%20OBC%20category.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Commission%20on%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Classes%20headed%20by%20G.D.%20Sharma%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202022%20report%2C%20the%20commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greaterkashmir.com%2Fkashmir%2Fpaddaris-kolis-a