20cricket%20team%20batting%20star%20became%20the%20first%20player%20in%20history%20to%20scored%20over%20700%20runs%20in%20a%20single%20edition%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20In%2011%20matches%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20scored%20765%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2095.62.%20Virat%20Kohli%20also%20scored%20three%20centuries%20and%20six%20half-centuries.%20Courtesy%20those%20tons%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20now%20placed%20only%20second%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20terms%20of%20most%20international%20centuries.%20While%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20has%20100%20international%20tons%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%2080.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20is%2035%20now%20and%20supremely%20fit%20but%20West%20Indies%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Brian%20Lara%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F269-brian-lara-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBrian%20Lara%3C%2Fa%3E%20believes%20that%20getting%20to%20100%20tons%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20Virat%20Kohli%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20old%20is%20Kohli%20now%3F%2035%2C%20right%3F%20He%20has%2080%20but%20still%20needs%2020.%20If%20he%20scores%20five%20centuries%20every%20year%20he'd%20need%20four%20more%20years%20to%20equal%20Tendulkar.%20Kohli%20will%20be%2039%20then.%20Tough%20job%2C%20very%20tough%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Lara%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anandabazar.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fexclusive-interview-of-west-indian-cricketer-brian-lara-at-kolkata%2Fcid%2F1478611%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnandabazar%20Patrika%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan't%20say%20with%20certainty%2C%20no%20one%20can.%20Those%20saying%20are%20not%20using%20cricketing%20logic.%2020%20centuries%20seem%20a%20long%20way%20away.%20Most%20cricketers%20can't%20score%20that%20in%20their%20entire%20career.%20I%20won't%20be%20adventurous%20and%20say%20Kohli%20will%20do%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAge%20doesn't%20stop%20for%20anyone.%20Kohli%20will%20break%20many%20more%20records%20but%20100%3Cbr%3E%5Cncenturies%20seems%20the%20most%20difficult%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrian%20Lara%20added%20that%20he%20is%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Virat%20Kohli's%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20Kohli%20can%20come%20close.%20I'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20his%20discipline%20and%20dedication.%20The%20way%20he%20prepares%20for%20a%20match%20by%20giving%20it%20his%20all%E2%80%A6%20how%20can%20you%20not%20be%20his%20fan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20best%20wishes%20are%20with%20him.%20I'd%20be%20very%20happy%20if%20he%20could%20score%20100%20centuries%20like%20Tendulkar.%20Sachin%20was%20a%20dear%20friend%20and%20like%20I%20said%20before%2C%20I'm%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Kohli.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20finest%20batters%20of%20this%20generation%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20stare%20at%20a%20an%20undecisive%20future%20in%20white-ball%20cricket.%20The%20two%20haven't%20featured%20in%20a%20T20%20international%20since%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202022%20and%20aren't%20part%20of%20India's%20plans%20for%20the%20South%20Africa%20assignment%20too.%20As%20debate%20rages%20on%20in%20the%20cricketing%20fraternity%20over%20their%20potential%20T20%20return%2C%20opinions%20are%20divided.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20Manjrekar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41124-sanjay-vijay-manjrekar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Manjrekar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20India%20cricketer%2C%20feels%20a%20call%20should%20be%20taken%20on%20the%20duo's%20participation%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20closer