eshow%2F105815942.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20Fights%20Extradition%20to%20US%20in%20Czech%20Court%2C%20Fate%20of%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%20Will%20Turn%20on%20Outcome%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07165428%2FPassport_front_cover.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20the%20Indian%20national%20indicted%20by%20federal%20prosecutors%C2%A0in%20the%20United%20States%C2%A0for%20plotting%20to%20assassinate%20a%20Sikh%20American%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%2C%20has%20appealed%20a%20Prague%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20allowing%20his%20extradition%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Czech%20judicial%20officials%20told%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eon%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20announced%20that%20they%20had%20charged%20Gupta%20with%20%E2%80%98murder%20for%20hire%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98conspiracy%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20ultimately%20failed%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20Sikh%20activist%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20filed%20charges%20accused%20an%20unnamed%20but%20%E2%80%9Cidentified%20Indian%20government%20official%E2%80%9D%20of%20recruiting%20Gupta%20to%20hire%20a%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99.%20The%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%20that%20Gupta%20thought%20he%20was%20hiring%20was%20actually%20an%20undercover%20US%20law%20enforcement%20officer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20target%20was%20also%20unnamed%20in%20the%20court%20documents%20but%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FMcOUf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentified%20by%20media%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20general%20counsel%20for%20the%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%20a%20Khalistan%20advocacy%20group%20that%20is%20proscribed%20in%20India.%20Pannun%20is%20a%20US%20citizen%20who%20also%20holds%20Canadian%20nationality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20was%20arrested%20in%20Prague%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20US%20authorities%20when%20he%20arrived%20there%20from%20India%20on%20June%2030%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Czech%20ministry%20of%20justice%20spokesperson%20Vladimir%20%C5%98epka%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Etold%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20municipal%20court%20in%20Prague%20had%20issued%20an%20order%20on%20November%2023%20on%20the%20admissibility%20of%20the%20extradition%20order%20to%20the%20United%20States.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20municipal%20court%20is%20not%20yet%20in%20legal%20force.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20for%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20delay%20in%20implementing%20the%20order%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Gupta%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20(i.e.%20an%20ordinary%20remedy)%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20municipal%20court%20in%20Prague%20on%20the%20admissibility%20of%20extradition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20step%20would%20be%20a%20referral%20to%20the%20high%20court%20for%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20complaint%20by%20Gupta.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20high%20court%20in%20Prague%20shall%20either%20dismiss%20the%20complaint%20and%20thus%20uphold%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20municipal%20court%2C%20revoke%20the%20challenged%20decision%20and%20refer%20the%20case%20back%20to%20the%20municipal%20court%20in%20Prague%20for%20a%20new%20hearing%2C%20or%20change%20the%20decision%20and%20rule%20on%20the%20inadmissibility%20of%20the%20extradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Repka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20contact%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20defence%20counsel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Manhattan%20indictment%20also%20suggested%20that%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20co-conspirator%20%E2%80%93%20the%20unnamed%20Indian%20government%20official%20%E2%80%93%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20assassination%20of%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20separatist%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20in%20June.%20When%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20India%20of%20involvement%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20in%20mid-September%2C%20it%20triggered%20a%20strong%20reaction%20from%20India%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20recall%20of%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20the%20suspension%20of%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20since%20resumed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fd9%2F2023-11%2Fu.s._v._gupta_indictment.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20US%20prosecutors%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Gupta%2C%20described%20as%20a%20trafficker%20of%20drugs%20and%20weapons%2C%20had%20been%20recruited%20by%20the%20unnamed%20Indian%20government%20official%20(%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99)%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20After%20he%20agreed%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%2C%20Gupta%20was%20reportedly%20assured%20that%20a%20criminal%20case%20against%20him%20in%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%9Chad%20been%20taken%20care%20of%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20behalf%20of%20%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99%2C%20Gupta%2C%20who%20was%20based%20in%20India%2C%20contacted%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20associate%E2%80%9D%20who%20was%20actually%20an%20informer%20for%20the%20US%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Agency.%20In%20turn%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98associate%E2%80%99%20introduced%20him%20to%20a%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20was%20an%20undercover%20officer%20deployed%20by%20the%20DEA%20and%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20as%20per%20the%20filed%20charges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Fus-attorney-announces-charges-connection-foiled-plot-assassinate-us-citizen-new-york%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20indictment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20that%20Gupta%20travelled%20from%20India%20to%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20on%20June%2030.%20%E2%80%9CUpon%20arrival%2C%20Gupta%20was%20arrested%20by%20Czech%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20his%20participation%20in%20the%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20the%20Victim%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%20The%2015-page%20document%20did%20not%20give%20any%20more%20details%20about%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20stay%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30010249%2Findictment-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687016%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20a%20still%20image%20ofthe%20Advance%20Payment%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20DoJ%20indictment%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20and%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProceedings%20against%20Gupta%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20able%20to%20piece%20together%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20against%20Gupta%20in%20the%20Central%20European%20nation%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Czech%20justice%20ministry%2C%20Gupta%20was%20taken%20into%20%E2%80%9Cprovisional%20custody%20on%20the%20request%20of%20the%20competent%20authority%20of%20the%20US%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20formal%20request%20for%20extradition%20was%20submitted%20by%20US%20authorities%20in%20August%202023.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20extradition%20of%20Mr%20Gupta%20was%20requested%20for%20the%20crime%20of%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder%20for%20hire%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20request%20was%20then%20passed%20on%20to%20the%20state%20prosecutor%2C%20who%20then%20began%20a%20preliminary%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20queries%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Ale%C5%A1%20Cimbala%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20municipal%20public%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20Prague%2C%20confirmed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpreliminary%20investigation%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20conducted%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Act%20on%20International%20Judicial%20Cooperation%20in%20Criminal%20Matters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98preliminary%20investigation%E2%80%99%20is%20not%20to%20examine%20and%20assess%20the%20facts%20to%20reach%20a%20conclusion%20of%20guilt%20or%20innocence%2C%20but%20only%20to%20verify%20whether%20there%20are%20any%20legal%20obstacles%20in%20the%20case%20that%20would%20prevent%20the%20extradition%20of%20a%20person%20to%20a%20foreign%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECimbala%20replied%20in%20Czech%20to%20a%20set%20of%20written%20questions%20submitted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20For%20the%20purposes%20of%20this%20article%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20used%20a%20machine%20translation%20of%20his%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20%E2%80%98preliminary%20investigation%E2%80%99%2C%20Cimbala%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%2C%20on%20October%204%2C%202023%2C%20the%20public%20prosecutor%20of%20the%20local%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%20submitted%20a%20motion%20to%20declare%20the%20extradition%20admissible%20to%20the%20Municipal%20Court%20in%20Prague%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ruling%20of%20the%20municipal%20court%20came%20seven%20weeks%20after%20the%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20motion%20was%20filed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20ruled%20on%20the%20application%20in%20open%20court%20on%2023%20November%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELess%20than%20a%20week%20after%20the%20Prague%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20prosecutors%20filed%20a%20new%20detailed%2C%20and%20unsealed%20indictment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20New%20York%2C%20which%20declared%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20had%20been%20arrested%20by%20Czech%20authorities.%20Hours%20before%20the%20indictment%20was%20filed%2C%20India%20announced%20that%20a%20high-level%20inquiry%20committee%20had%20been%20looking%20into%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20information%20since%20November%2018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20extradition%20process%20moving%20to%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20Cimbala%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnext%20procedural%20procedure%20is%20now%20taking%20place%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20on%20the%20admissibility%20of%20extradition%20comes%20into%20force%2C%20the%20presiding%20judge%20of%20the%20court%20will%20refer%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Justice%2C%20as%20the%20Minister%20of%20Justice%20has%20other%20subsequent%20powers%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20international%20judicial%20cooperation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20justice%20ministry%20representative%20also%20reiterated%20that%20once%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdecision%20on%20the%20admissibility%20of%20the%20extradition%20is%20in%20legal%20force%2C%E2%80%9D%20then%20the%20file%20would%20be%20referred%20to%20his%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%2C%20in%20general%2C%20the%20minister%20is%20bound%20by%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20competent%20court%20rules%20on%20the%20inadmissibility%20of%20the%20extradition%2C%20then%20the%20Minister%20of%20Justice%20is%20bound%20by%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20court%20and%20may%20not%20authorise%20the%20extradition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20spokesperson%20%C5%98epka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20US%20granted%20access%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%2C%20however%2C%20uncertain%20whether%20the%20US%20had%20requested%20or%20been%20granted%20access%20to%20Gupta%20during%20the%20processing%20of%20the%20extradition%20request.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20answer%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20question%20about%20access%20to%20Gupta%2C%20%C5%98epka%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Esaid%20that%20interrogation%20of%20Gupta%20by%20any%20foreign%20authority%20would%20be%20possible%20solely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20formal%20request%20for%20legal%20assistance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20case%2C%20there%20is%20%5Ba%5D%20pre-trial%20proceeding%20being%20conducted%20in%20a%20foreign%20state%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Public%20Prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20Office%20is%20competent%20to%20accept%20a%20request%20of%20the%20foreign%20authority%20for%20legal%20assistance%3B%20otherwise%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Justice%20is%20competent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20he%20added%20that%20the%20Czech%20justice%20ministry%20%E2%80%9Chas%20not%20received%20any%20formal%20requests%20for%20legal%20assistance%20concerning%20the%20interrogation%20of%20Mr%20Gupta%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20same%20question%20was%20posed%20to%20the%20Public%20Prosecutor%20General%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wir%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ee%20was%20told%20that%20no%20comments%20could%20be%20provided%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwhole%20extradition%20proceedings%E2%80%9D%20are%20the%20%E2%80%9Cexclusive%20competence%20of%20Ministry%20of%20Justice%20of%20the%20Czech%20Republic%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Czech%20justice%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%2C%20however%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20%E2%80%9Cuntil%20the%20decision%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20minister%20of%20justice%20on%20granting%20the%20extradition%2C%20the%20person%20whose%20extradition%20is%20sought%20may%20not%20be%20taken%20into%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20requesting%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98No%20record%20of%20Gupta%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20police%20in%20Gujarat%20have%20denied%20knowledge%20of%20any%20case%20being%20registered%20against%20Gupta%20in%20the%20state.%20Similarly%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20mention%20of%20him%20in%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovern