tle%22%3A%22Climate%20Change%20in%20Mind%2C%20India%20Masters%20Unique%20Breeder%20Nuclear%20Reactors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20world%20tries%20to%20find%20solutions%20for%20curbing%20carbon%20emissions%20that%20are%20blamed%20for%20causing%20climate%20change%2C%20the%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20(COP-28)%20taking%20place%20at%20Dubai%20is%20debating%20how%20to%20control%20use%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%20the%20main%20culprit%20for%20causing%20climate%20change%2C%20today%20the%20deployment%20of%20atomic%20energy%20which%20is%20source%20of%20carbon%20free%20electricity%20is%20finding%20more%20acceptability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20already%20has%20a%20highly%20advanced%20atomic%20energy%20programme%20and%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20control%20carbon%20emissions%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20triple%20generation%20of%20carbon%20free%20nuclear%20energy%20to%2022%2C000%20megawatts%20by%202032%20up%20from%20the%20nearly%207000%20megawatts%20at%20present.%20India's%20science%20minister%2C%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20told%20the%20Parliament%20yesterday%20that%20'nuclear%20power%20is%20considered%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20promising%20clean%20energy%20options%20for%20power%20generation%20in%20India's%20clean%20energy%20transition%20to%20meet%20the%20Net%20Zero%20target'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20focusing%20only%20on%20using%20uranium%20as%20the%20nuclear%20fuel%2C%20India%20is%20rapidly%20advancing%20to%20tap%20almost%20unlimited%20amounts%20of%20energy%20from%20plutonium%20and%20thorium.%20India%20has%20well%20established%20fast%20breeder%20nuclear%20reactor%20programme%20that%20can%20help%20provide%20the%20much%20needed%20'energy%20independence'%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20science%20minister%2C%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20asserts%20that%20%26quot%3Bnearly%209%20per%20cent%20share%20of%20electricity%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20contributed%20from%20India's%20nuclear%20sources%20by%20the%20year%202047.%20The%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20aims%20to%20achieve%2020%20GW%20capacity%20of%20nuclear%20power%20generation%20by%20the%20year%202030%20which%20will%20be%20a%20major%20milestone%20placing%20India%20as%20the%20third-largest%20producer%20of%20atomic%20energy%20in%20the%20world%20after%20the%20USA%20and%20France.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20the%20charge%20is%20a%20facility%20situated%20in%20a%20small%20town%20of%20Kalpakkam%2C%20not%20far%20from%20the%20world-famous%20UNESCO%20heritage%20site%20of%20Mahabalipuram%2C%20hundreds%20of%20Indian%20engineers%20are%20toiling%20hard%20to%20master%20the%20fast%20breeder%20reactor%20technology.%20NDTV's%20Science%20Editor%20Pallava%20Bagla%20was%20given%20rare%20access%20to%20visit%20the%20laboratories%20where%20Indian%20scientists%20are%20labouring%20to%20understand%20the%20complexities%20of%20using%20plutonium%20and%20thorium%20as%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fq36kp97_fast-breeder-reactor-india_625x300_07_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20layers%20of%20intense%20security%20that%20one%20has%20to%20pass%20through%20before%20entering%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20fast%20breeder%20reactor%20program.%20This%20is%20understandable%20since%20today%20only%20two%20countries%20Russia%20and%20India%20operate%20a%20functional%20fast%20breeder%20reactor%20since%20the%20technology%20is%20complex%20and%20very%20hard%20to%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fast%20breeder%20reactor%20is%20very%20unique%20and%20to%20a%20lay%20person%20it%20these%20defy%20basic%20logic%2C%20since%20these%20breeder%20reactors%20produce%20more%20fuel%20than%20they%20consume%20and%20that%20is%20what%20makes%20some%20describe%20these%20as%20the%20'akshaya%20patra'%20or%20the%20endless%20sources%20of%20producing%20energy.%20The%20word%20'fast'%20in%20these%20reactors%20comes%20from%20the%20use%20of%20high%20energy%20fast%20neutrons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20a%20functional%20Fast%20Breeder%20Test%20Reactor%20(FBTR)%20that%20has%20been%20functioning%20for%20the%20last%2038%20years.%20This%20tiny%20experimental%20reactor%20is%20the%20test%20bed%20where%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20perfected%20the%20use%20of%20advanced%20nuclear%20fuels.%20No%20country%20is%20willing%20to%20share%20the%20knowhow%20of%20this%20sensitive%20technology%2C%20and%20as%20a%20consequence%20scientists%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Center%20for%20Atomic%20Research%20(IGCAR)%2C%20Kalpakkam%20have%20learnt%20it%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20(DAE)%2C%20the%20Fast%20Breeder%20Test%20Reactor%20(FBTR)%20is%20a%2040MWt%2F%2013.6%20MWe%2C%20loop%20type%2C%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20sodium%20cooled%20fast%20reactor%20using%20a%20mixture%20of%20plutonium%20carbide%20and%20uranium%20carbide%20as%20the%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFBTR%20attained%20first%20criticality%20on%20October%2018%2C%201985%20and%20completed%2038%20years%20of%20successful%20operation%20on%20October%2018%2C%202023.%20Fast%20Breeder%20Test%20Reactor%20(FBTR)%20continues%20as%20the%20flagship%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Centre%20for%20Atomic%20Research%20(IGCAR)%20which%20is%20dedicated%20to%20fast%20reactor%20research%20in%20the%20second%20stage%20of%20the%20Indian%20nuclear%20power%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DAE%20says%20FBTR%20has%20crossed%20many%20milestones%20including%20operation%20of%20the%20plant%20at%20it%20design%20power%20of%2040%20MWt.%20Being%20a%20test%20reactor%2C%20its%20main%20objective%20is%20to%20operate%20on%20mission%20mode%20irradiation%20campaigns.%20FBTR%20has%20completed%2032%20irradiation%20campaigns%20and%20thirty-eight%20years%20of%20safe%20and%20successful%20operation%2C%20since%20its%20inception%20and%20is%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20fast%20breeder%20reactor%20and%20associated%20closed%20fuel%20cycle%20technologies.%20FBTR%20has%20been%20relicensed%20for%20operation%20up%20to%20June%2028%2C%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20experience%20and%20expertise%20gained%20by%20the%20successful%20operation%20of%20FBTR%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20embarked%20upon%20the%20design%20of%20500%20MWe%2C%20Prototype%20Fast%20Breeder%20Reactor%20(PFBR)%20which%20is%20now%20in%20an%20advanced%20stage%20of%20integrated%20commissioning.%20Mr%20G%20Shanmugam%2C%20Station%20Director%2C%20Fast%20Breeder%20Test%20Reactor%20(FBTR)%2C%20Kalpakkam%20says%20%26quot%3Bif%20all%20goes%20well%20the%20most%20advanced%20nuclear%20reactor%20of%20India%20the%20PFBR%20may%20commence%20operation%20in%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20next%20big%20experiment%2C%20scientists%20at%20IGCAR%20are%20exploring%20the%20feasibility%20of%20clean%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20production%20from%20FBTR%20since%20the%20plant%20already%20produces%20steam%20at%20very%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20is%20now%20getting%20ready%20to%20commission%20its%20ultra-modern%20indigenously%20designed%20and%20locally%20mastered%20big%20fast%20breeder%20reactor.%20It%20is%20only%20in%20fairy%20tales%20that%20one%20hears%20of%20a%20stove%20or%20a%20chulha%2C%20which%20even%20as%20it%20burns%20it%20also%20continuously%20and%20automatically%20makes%20more%20fuel%2C%20giving%20almost%20unhindered%20supply%20of%20energy.%20Yes%2C%20these%20new%20reactors%20seem%20magical%20but%20like%20all%20fairies%20or%20genies%20they%20are%20also%20very%20hard%20to%20tame%20and%20take%20control%20off.%20But%20an%20energy%20hungry%20India%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20master%20this%20genie.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701951000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F29manvt_atomic-energy_625x300_07_D