0musical%20force%20of%20nature%20the%20%26quot%3Bhero%20of%20her%20own%20story.%26quot%3B%20The%20huge%20%2492.8%20million%20opening%20earlier%20this%20year%20of%20Taylor%20Swift's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Eras%20Tour%26quot%3B%20film%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BCruel%20Summer%26quot%3B%20singer's%202023.%20Now%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20singer%20stated%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20career%20death%26quot%3B%20when%20Kim%20Kardashian%20leaked%20her%20phone%20call%20with%20rapper%20Kanye%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Kim%20Kardashian%20shared%20audio%20and%20video%20of%20her%20then-husband%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20talking%20on%20call%20in%20which%20the%20pop%20singer%20seemed%20to%20endorse%20the%20words%20that%20the%20rapper%20had%20written%20about%20her%20in%20his%20song.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20me%20and%20Taylor%20might%20still%20have%20sex%20%2F%20I%20made%20that%20b****%20famous%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20West%20wrote%20in%20the%20song.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Ms%20Swift%20refuted%20rumours%20that%20the%20singer%20had%20ever%20approved%20of%20the%20song's%20lyrics%20after%20it%20was%20released.%20There%20was%20no%20reference%20in%20the%20video%20where%20West%20claimed%20he%20%26quot%3Bmade%20her%20famous%26quot%3B%20or%20that%20he%20would%20call%20Swift%20a%20%26quot%3Bb****%26quot%3B%20when%20an%20unedited%20version%20of%20the%20conversation%20was%20made%20public%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20singer%20added%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20career%20death%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20appeared%20that%20she%20had%20approved%20the%20lyrics.%20%26quot%3BMake%20no%20mistake%20-%20my%20career%20was%20taken%20away%20from%20me.%20You%20have%20a%20fully%20manufactured%20frame%20job%2C%20in%20an%20illegally%20recorded%20phone%20call%2C%20which%20Kim%20Kardashian%20edited%20and%20then%20put%20out%20to%20say%20to%20everyone%20that%20I%20was%20a%20liar%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6342806%2Fperson-of-the-year-2023-taylor-swift%2F%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20affected%20her%20mentally%20and%20she%20even%20moved%20to%20a%20new%20place%20to%20hide%20from%20all%20the%20attention.%20%26quot%3BThat%20took%20me%20down%20psychologically%20to%20a%20place%20I've%20never%20been%20before.%20I%20moved%20to%20a%20foreign%20country.%20I%20didn't%20leave%20a%20rental%20house%20for%20a%20year.%20I%20was%20afraid%20to%20get%20on%20phone%20calls.%20I%20pushed%20away%20most%20people%20in%20my%20life%20because%20I%20didn't%20trust%20anyone%20anymore.%20I%20went%20down%20really%2C%20really%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BLover%26quot%3B%20singer%20told%20Time%20Magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BAll%20Too%20Well%26quot%3B%20singer%20initially%20seemed%20to%20accuse%20the%20rapper%20and%20his%20then-wife%20of%20%26quot%3Bediting%20and%20manipulating%26quot%3B%20portions%20of%20the%20phone%20call%20that%20had%20surfaced%20in%202016%2C%20until%20in%20March%202020%2C%20when%20the%20entire%20phone%20conversation%20between%20Ms%20Swift%20and%20Mr%20West%20emerged%20online.%20In%20one%20of%20her%20Instagram%20stories%20about%20donations%20to%20charities%2C%20the%20singer%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20answering%20those%20who%20are%20asking%20how%20I%20feel%20about%20the%20video%20footage%20that%20leaked%2C%20proving%20that%20I%20was%20telling%20the%20truth%20the%20whole%20time%20about%20*that%20call*%20(you%20know%2C%20the%20one%20that%20was%20illegally%20recorded%2C%20that%20somebody%20edited%20and%20manipulated%20in%20order%20to%20frame%20me%20and%20put%20me%2C%20my%20family%20and%20fans%20through%20hell%20for%20four%20years)...SWIPE%20UP%20to%20see%20what%20really%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20same%2C%20the%20SKIMS%20founder%20wrote%20on%20Twitter%2C%20%26quot%3B%40taylorswift13%20has%20chosen%20to%20reig