%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20accounted%20for%20in%20the%20vegetarian%20thali%20is%20vegetables%20(onion%2C%20tomato%2C%20and%20potato)%2C%20rice%2C%20dal%2C%20curd%2C%20and%20salad.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20for%20representational%20purposes%2C%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20consists%20of%20all%20the%20above%20constituents%2C%20but%20the%20dal%20is%20replaced%20by%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20differential%20rise%20in%20vegetarian%20and%20non-vegetarian%20thalis%20is%20due%20to%20the%20marginal%201%25%20to%203%25%20slash%20in%20prices%20of%20broilers%2C%20which%20account%20for%2050%25%20of%20the%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20cost.%20While%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20rose%20from%20Rs%2058.2%20in%20October%20to%20Rs%2061.2%20in%20November%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20preparing%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20jumped%20to%20Rs%2030.3%20in%20November%20from%20Rs%2027.5%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20vegetarian%20thali%20rose%209%25%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20a%2093%25%20rise%20in%20onion%20prices%20and%20a%2015%25%20jump%20in%20tomato%20prices.%20The%20prices%20of%20pulses%20also%20jumped%20by%2021%25%20over%20the%20last%20year.%C2%A0The%20analysis%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20input%20prices%20of%20ingredients%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20family%20of%20five%20would%20incur%20an%20additional%20cost%20of%20Rs%2014%20for%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%2C%20and%20Rs%2015%20for%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali.%20Assuming%20that%20they%20prepare%20a%20thali%20for%20both%20lunch%20and%20dinner%2C%20it%20could%20additionally%20cost%20them%20Rs%20840%20per%20month%20for%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%2C%20and%20Rs%20900%20per%20month%20for%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali.%20The%20total%20cost%20of%20preparing%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20for%20a%20five-member%20family%20would%20be%20Rs%204%2C545%20per%20month%20and%20for%20a%20non-vegetarian%20thali%