u-mithai-bakarwadi-babasaheb-bhaskar-ganesh-chitale-shrikhand-mango-burfi-peda-indian-icons-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilk%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20cottage%20cheese%2C%20shrikhand%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20etc.%20Today%2C%20over%2040%2C000%20farmers%20work%20with%20the%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bakarwadi%20sold%20by%20the%20brand%20is%20so%20famous%20that%20over%201%2C000%20kgs%20are%20made%20in%20an%20hour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Vadilal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20all%20enjoyed%20the%20popsicles%20on%20a%20sunny%20afternoon%20after%20the%20end-of-year%20exams.%20The%20name%20%E2%80%98Vadilal%E2%80%99%20evokes%20nostalgia.%20The%20brand%20had%20humble%20beginnings%20in%20Gujarat%20in%201907.%20At%20the%20time%20their%20ice%20creams%20were%20made%20using%20the%20traditional%20and%20popular%20Kothi%20method%20in%20which%20a%20hand-operated%20machine%20was%20used%20to%20churn%20milk%2C%20ice%20and%20salt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVadilal%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271527%2Fcentury-old-vadilal-ice-cream-brand-first-to-launch-dollies-cones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20the%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sodas%20but%20it%20was%20his%20son%20Ranchod%20Lal%20Gandhi%20who%20introduced%20ice%20creams%20to%20the%20brand.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%2C%20the%20company%20had%20opened%20four%20outlets%20across%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20company%20clocked%20a%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%201%2C%20071%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700662404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fjaswantiben-popat-lijjat-papad-owner-story-1700660151.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Parle-G%20to%20Lijjat%20Papad%2C%20these%20iconic%20food%20businesses%20of%20India%20had%20humble%20beginnings%20and%20inspiring%20stories%20that%20led%20to%20their%20success%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334682%2Flegacy-food-businesses-nilon-parle-g-balaji-wafers-ravalgaon-multicrore%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Droughts%20Led%20to%20Losses%2C%20Oyster%20Pearl%20Farming%20Helped%20Marathwada%20Farmers%20Reap%20Huge%20Profits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20uncertain%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20irrigation%20canals%20completely%20drying%20up%2C%20cultivation%20in%20the%20parched%20land%20of%20the%20Osmanabad%20district%20has%20become%20exhausting%20for%20farmers.%20Lying%20under%20the%20rain%20shadow%20region%20of%20Marathwada%2C%20the%20district%20faces%20acute%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20input%20costs%20and%20unfair%20market%20prices%20have%20severely%20affected%20the%20output%20and%20yield%20of%20the%20major%20crops%20of%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20like%20soybean%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20millet.%20The%20compounding%20debts%20put%20Maharashtra%20farmers%20under%20a%20huge%20economic%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20recurring%20droughts%20force%20farmers%20to%20sometimes%20end%20their%20lives.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F169599016203ADSI-2021Chapter-2Suicides-ExcludingFarmerCauses.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENCRB%3C%2Fa%3E)%20data%3C%2Fem%3E%20revealed%20that%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C881%20persons%20involved%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%202021.%20With%2037.3%20percent%2C%20Maharashtra%20accounted%20for%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20farmer%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20impoverished%20farmers%20have%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20oyster%20pearls%20in%20the%20water-starved%20Marathwada%20to%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20recurring%20droughts%20and%20low%20crop%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20farmer%20is%20Sanjay%20Narsing%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20nine%20other%20small-scale%20farmers%2C%20Sanjay%20harvested%208%2C000%20pearls%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20pond%2C%20earning%20them%20Rs%2040%20lakh.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229545%2Fagra-woman-entrepreneur-grow-oysters-pearl-farming-home-earn-lakhs-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoyster%20pearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20group%20of%20farmers%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334696%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20group%20of%20farmers%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20by%20selling%208%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHarvesting%20pearls%20in%20water-scarce%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20pursuing%20a%20Diploma%20in%20Medical%20Laboratory%20Technology%20(DMLT)%2C%20Sanjay%20works%20part-time%20as%20a%20lab%20assistant.%20But%20farming%20comes%20naturally%20to%20him%20as%20for%20generations%2C%20his%20family%20has%20been%20cultivating%20traditional%20crops.%20However%2C%20agriculture%20hardly%20reaped%20the%20family%20any%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20year%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20rain%20at%20all.%20We%20did%20sow%20soybeans%20and%20other%20crops%2C%20but%20we%20did%20not%20get%20any%20output.%20It%20has%20become%20difficult%20to%20even%20earn%20back%20the%20input%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20even%20established%20a%20water%20bank%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20land%20for%20irrigation%20purposes.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20fish%20farming%20to%20utilise%20the%20water%20bank%20but%20the%20initiative%20was%20dead%20in%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFish%20farming%20did%20not%20prove%20profitable%20for%20us%20as%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20input%20costs.%20If%20we%20sold%20a%20fish%20for%20Rs%20100%2C%20we%20would%20incur%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2080.%20We%20were%20only%20left%20with%20Rs%2020%20profit.%20It%20was%20very%20little%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Sanjay%20came%20across%20a%20news%20report%20that%20mentioned%20the%20profitability%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming.%20Motivated%20to%20try%20his%20hands%20in%20cultivating%20oysters%2C%20he%20bought%2025%2C000%20oysters%20to%20cultivate%20in%20his%20water%20bank.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20also%20roped%20in